3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Transfer entropy is a statistical method used to quantify dependencies in complex systems datasets, which is a common task in machine learning. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - While not the main focus of the paper, the authors do mention using software packages for their analysis.
